58.6	Howard_Rheingold	Howard Rheingold	Howard Rheingold (born July 7, 1947) is a critic, writer, and teacher; his specialties are on the cultural, social and political implications of modern communication media such as the Internet, mobile telephony and virtual communities (a term he is credited with inventing).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/49/HowardRheingoldJI4.jpg/220px-HowardRheingoldJI4.jpg
